CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY CHTR.DA_ELECTRONIC_CHANNEL_INST
/* Generated on 20-JAN-15 03.39.50.847340000 PM -06:00 */
AS

FUNCTION add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,elec_address_id IN NUMBER
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
) RETURN NUMBER
IS
l_return_pk NUMBER;
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_electronic_channel_inst.add(fx), parms=' || elec_address_id || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_electronic_channel_inst a
(
a.elec_address_channel_inst_id
,a.elec_address_id
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)
VALUES
(
chtr.s_elec_address_channel_inst_id.NEXTVAL
,add.elec_address_id
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP
,add.audit_user
,NULL
,NULL
) RETURNING a.elec_address_channel_inst_id INTO l_return_pk;
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_electronic_channel_inst.add(fx)');
RETURN l_return_pk;

END add;

process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec

)
IS
BEGIN

INSERT INTO chtr.t_electronic_channel_inst a
(
a.elec_address_channel_inst_id
,a.elec_address_id
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)

(
chtr.s_elec_address_channel_inst_id.NEXTVAL
,add.elec_address_id
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP

,NULL
,NULL
);
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_electronic_channel_inst.add');

END add;

add.elec_address_channel_inst_id

PROCEDURE del (

)
IS
BEGIN

SET a.record_stat = 'D'
,a.modified_dttm = SYSTIMESTAMP
,a.modified_by = del.audit_user
